### NPFS HTTP API 测试文件
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件或 IntelliJ IDEA 运行
### 确保 HTTP 服务已启动：go run . -http-server

@baseUrl = http://121.41.129.227:19870
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### ====================================
### 健康检查
### ====================================

# @name healthCheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### ====================================
### 目录操作
### ====================================

### 1. 检查目录是否存在
# @name checkDir
POST {{apiUrl}}/dir/check
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

path=/npcdata/t/

### 2. 创建目录（递归）
# @name createDirRecursive
POST {{apiUrl}}/dir/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "/my_files",
  "recursive": true
}

### 3. 创建目录（不递归）
# @name createDir
POST {{apiUrl}}/dir/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "/my_files/subdir",
  "recursive": false
}

### 4. 列出目录内容
# @name listDirRoot
GET {{apiUrl}}/dir/list?path=/npcdata/

### 5. 列出指定目录
# @name listDirMyFiles
GET {{apiUrl}}/dir/list?path=/my_files

### 6. 删除目录（递归、强制）
# @name deleteDirRecursive
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/dir/delete?path=/test&recursive=true&force=true

### 7. 删除目录（非递归）
# @name deleteDir
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/dir/delete?path=/test&recursive=false&force=true

### ====================================
### 文件操作
### ====================================

### 8. 读取文件内容
# @name readFile
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/read?path=/my_files/hello.txt

### 9. 保存文本内容到文件
# @name saveFile
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello World from HTTP API!",
  "dir": "/my_files",
  "filename": "hello.txt"
}

### 10. 保存 JSON 内容到文件
# @name saveJsonFile
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "{\n  \"name\": \"test\",\n  \"value\": 123\n}",
  "dir": "/my_files",
  "filename": "data.json"
}

### 11. 上传本地文件
### 注意：需要修改文件路径为实际存在的文件
# @name uploadFile
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="./test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

这是测试文件内容
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="dir"

/uploads
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="filename"

uploaded.txt
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 12. 下载文件
# @name downloadFile
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/download?path=/my_files/hello.txt

### 13. 下载文件并指定文件名
# @name downloadFileWithFilename
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/download?path=/my_files/hello.txt&filename=downloaded.txt

### 14. 删除文件
# @name deleteFile
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/file/delete?path=/npcdata/1.txt&force=true

### ====================================
### 完整测试流程
### ====================================

### 步骤 1: 创建测试目录
# @name testStep1
POST {{apiUrl}}/dir/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "/http_test",
  "recursive": true
}

### 步骤 2: 保存测试文件
# @name testStep2
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "这是 HTTP API 测试文件的内容\n第二行内容\n第三行内容",
  "dir": "/http_test",
  "filename": "test.txt"
}

### 步骤 3: 检查目录
# @name testStep3
POST {{apiUrl}}/dir/check
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

path=/http_test

### 步骤 4: 列出目录
# @name testStep4
GET {{apiUrl}}/dir/list?path=/http_test

### 步骤 5: 读取文件
# @name testStep5
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/read?path=/http_test/test.txt

### 步骤 6: 删除文件
# @name testStep6
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/file/delete?path=/http_test/test.txt&force=true

### 步骤 7: 删除目录
# @name testStep7
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/dir/delete?path=/http_test&recursive=true&force=true

### ====================================
### 批量操作示例
### ====================================

### 批量创建多个文件
# @name batchCreateFiles
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "批量创建的文件 1",
  "dir": "/batch_test",
  "filename": "file1.txt"
}

### 批量创建文件 2
# @name batchCreateFiles2
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "批量创建的文件 2",
  "dir": "/batch_test",
  "filename": "file2.txt"
}

### 批量创建文件 3
# @name batchCreateFiles3
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "批量创建的文件 3",
  "dir": "/batch_test",
  "filename": "file3.txt"
}

### ====================================
### 错误处理示例
### ====================================

### 尝试读取不存在的文件
# @name readNonExistentFile
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/read?path=/not_exists/file.txt

### 尝试创建已存在的目录
# @name createExistingDir
POST {{apiUrl}}/dir/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "/my_files",
  "recursive": true
}

### 缺少必需参数
# @name missingParam
POST {{apiUrl}}/file/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "缺少 dir 和 filename 参数"
}

### ====================================
### cURL 命令示例（仅供参考）
### ====================================

### cURL: 健康检查
# curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/health

### cURL: 创建目录
# curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/dir/create \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"path":"/test","recursive":true}'

### cURL: 保存文件
# curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/file/save \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"content":"Hello","dir":"/test","filename":"hello.txt"}'

### cURL: 读取文件
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:8080/api/v1/file/read?path=/test/hello.txt"

### cURL: 列出目录
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:8080/api/v1/dir/list?path=/test"

### cURL: 上传文件
# curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/file/upload \
#   -F "file=@./local.txt" \
#   -F "dir=/uploads" \
#   -F "filename=upload.txt"

### cURL: 下载文件
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:8080/api/v1/file/download?path=/test/hello.txt" -o downloaded.txt

### cURL: 删除文件
# curl -X DELETE "http://localhost:8080/api/v1/file/delete?path=/test/hello.txt&force=true"
